Package: trustOptim
Type: Package
Title: Trust region nonlinear optimization, efficient for sparse Hessians
Version: 0.8.5
Date: 2015-01-27
Authors@R: "Michael Braun <braunm@smu.edu> [aut, cre]"
URL: http://coxprofs.cox.smu.edu/braunm
Description: Trust region algorithm for nonlinear optimization. In addition to
    being more stable and robust than optim, this package includes
    methods that are scalable and efficient (in terms
    of both speed and memory usage) when the Hessian is sparse.
License: MPL (>= 2.0)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.2),
    Rcpp (>= 0.11.3),
    RcppEigen (>= 0.3.2.3),
    Matrix (>= 1.1.4)
Suggests:
    sparseHessianFD,
    testthat,
    knitr
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
Copyright: (c) 2015 Michael Braun
Roxygen: list(wrap=FALSE)
VignetteBuilder:  knitr
SystemRequirements:  C++11
